## Wrapping Up the First Week

I cannot believe the first week is almost done. Days 1 through 4 introduced me to each pillar of GRC individually — what governance means, how risk management works, and why compliance is the floor rather than the ceiling. Today felt like the pieces finally started connecting. Day 5 is about stepping back and seeing how Governance, Risk, and Compliance are not three separate things — they are one system, and they only work properly when they work together.

